    content: # PatternFly 5 → PatternFly 6: Comprehensive Migration Checklist

> Source: https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/ + release notes + pf-codemods README
> Generated: 2026-05-31

---

## Table of Contents
1. [Package & Dependency Changes](#1-package--dependency-changes)
2. [Component API Changes (Props Renamed/Removed)](#2-component-api-changes)
3. [Component Restructuring (Major Refactors)](#3-component-restructuring)
4. [CSS / Token / Variable Changes](#4-css--token--variable-changes)
5. [Icon Changes](#5-icon-changes)
6. [Chart Changes](#6-chart-changes)
7. [Import Path Changes](#7-import-path-changes)
8. [Removed / Deprecated Components](#8-removed--deprecated-components)
9. [New Required Patterns](#9-new-required-patterns)
10. [Test Impact & Breakages](#10-test-impact--breakages)
11. [Codemod Summary](#11-codemod-summary)

---

## 1. Package & Dependency Changes

### Version Bump
| What | Old | New | Codemod |
|------|-----|-----|---------|
| All `@patternfly/*` packages | v5.x | v6.x | **Manual** — update package.json before running codemods |
| CSS class prefix | `pf-v5-*` | `pf-v6-*` | **Yes** — `class-name-updater --v6 --fix` |
| React minimum version | React 17+ | React 18+ (recommended) | Manual |

### New Peer Dependencies
| Package | Change | Notes |
|---------|--------|-------|
| `victory` / `victory-core` / `victory-tooltip` | Now **optional** peer dependency of `@patternfly/react-charts` | Must be installed explicitly if using Victory-based charts |

### Package Renames / Moves
| Old Package/Path | New Package/Path | Codemod |
|------------------|------------------|---------|
| `@patternfly/react-charts` (direct) | `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` | **Yes** — `chartsImport-moved` |
| LogViewer CSS from `@patternfly/react-core` | CSS now in `@patternfly/react-log-viewer` itself | **No** — manual import update |

---

## 2. Component API Changes (Props Renamed/Removed)

### Props Renamed

| Component | Old Prop | New Prop | Codemod |
|-----------|----------|----------|---------|
| **AccordionToggle** | `isExpanded` (on AccordionToggle) | `isExpanded` (moved to AccordionItem) | **Yes** |
| **Avatar** | `border` | `isBordered` | **Yes** |
| **Banner** | `variant` | `color` or `status` (context-dependent) | **Yes** (may need manual review) |
| **Button** | `isActive` | `isClicked` | **Yes** |
| **Checkbox / Radio** | `isLabelBeforeButton` | `labelPosition="start"` | **Yes** |
| **ExpandableSection** | `isActive` | _(removed entirely)_ | **Yes** |
| **FormGroup** | `labelIcon` | `labelHelp` (use `FormGroupLabelHelp` element) | **Yes** |
| **Label** | `isOverflowLabel` | `variant="overflow"` | **Yes** |
| **Nav** | `variant="tertiary"` | `variant="horizontal-subnav"` | **Yes** |
| **Page** | `header` | `masthead` | **Yes** |
| **Page** | `isTertiaryNavGrouped` | `isHorizontalSubnavGrouped` | **Yes** |
| **Page** | `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` | `isHorizontalSubnavWidthLimited` | **Yes** |
| **Page** | `tertiaryNav` | `horizontalSubnav` | **Yes** |
| **Switch** | `labelOff` | _(removed — label should not change dynamically)_ | **Yes** |
| **Tabs** | `isSecondary` | `isSubtab` | **Yes** |
| **Tabs** | `variant="light300"` | `variant="secondary"` | **Yes** |
| **Toolbar align** | `"alignLeft"` / `"alignRight"` | `"alignStart"` / `"alignEnd"` | **Yes** |
| **Toolbar spacer** | `spacer` prop | `gap` / `columnGap` / `rowGap` | **Yes** |
| **Toolbar spacer** | `spaceItems` prop | _(removed)_ | **Yes** |
| **ToolbarChipGroupContent** | Component name | **ToolbarLabelGroupContent** | **Yes** |
| **ToolbarItem** | `variant="chip-group"` | `variant="label-group"` | **Yes** |
| **ToolbarItem** | `variant="bulk-select"` / `"overflow-menu"` / `"search-filter"` | _(removed)_ | **Yes** |

### Props Removed

| Component | Removed Prop | Notes | Codemod |
|-----------|-------------|-------|---------|
| **AccordionContent** | `isHidden` | Visibility now automatic from AccordionItem `isExpanded` | **Yes** |
| **Card** | Props for raised/clickable cards (multiple) | Clickable card API simplified | **Yes** |
| **Card** (clickable) | `selectableActions.selectableActionId`, `selectableActions.name` | No longer necessary for clickable-only cards | **Yes** |
| **DataListAction** | `isPlainButtonAction` | Wrapper no longer needed | **Yes** |
| **Drawer** | `hasNoPadding` (DrawerHead) | Removed | **Yes** |
| **ExpandableSection** | `isActive` | Removed | **Yes** |
| **HelperTextItem** | `hasIcon`, `isDynamic` | Icon auto-renders when variant ≠ "default" or icon prop passed | **Yes** |
| **Masthead** | `backgroundColor` | Theming no longer handled React-side | **Yes** |
| **Nav** | `theme` | Use light/dark mode theming instead | **Yes** |
| **NavItem** | `hasNavLinkWrapper` | Removed; use new `icon` prop for icons | **Yes** |
| **PageHeaderToolsItem** | `isSelected` | Removed | **Yes** |
| **PageSection** | `variant` values other than `"default"` or `"secondary"` | Removed (codemods set to default) | **Yes** |
| **PageSection** | `type="nav"` | Removed | **Yes** |
| **PageSidebar** | `theme` | Theming no longer handled React-side | **Yes** |
| **Toolbar** | Various props (multiple removed) | See #10674 | **Yes** |
| **WizardStep** | `body={null}` | No longer accepts null | **Yes** |

### Color Prop Updates

| Component | Old Value | New Value | Codemod |
|-----------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| **Banner, Label** | `"cyan"` | `"teal"` | **Yes** |
| **Banner, Label** | `"gold"` | `"yellow"` | **Yes** |
| **Drawer** (colorVariant) | `"light-200"` / `light200` enum | `"secondary"` / `secondary` enum | **Yes** |
| **DrawerContent** (colorVariant) | `"no-background"` | _(removed; new "primary" value added)_ | **Yes** |

---

## 3. Component Restructuring (Major Refactors)

### EmptyState — ⚠️ SIGNIFICANT CHANGE

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Structure | `EmptyState` + `EmptyStateHeader` + `EmptyStateIcon` as separate children | `EmptyState` renders header and icon **internally** via props | **Partial** — codemod handles exports, but manual work likely needed |
| `EmptyStateHeader` | Separate exported component | **No longer exported** — pass `headingText`, etc. as props to EmptyState | **Yes** (export fix) |
| `EmptyStateIcon` | Separate exported component | **No longer exported** — pass icon via `icon` prop on EmptyState | **Yes** (export fix) |
| Icon wrapping | Manual `<EmptyStateIcon icon={MyIcon} />` | Content passed to `icon` prop auto-wrapped by EmptyStateIcon | **Partial** |

**Manual work required:** Review all EmptyState usages. Complex customizations may not be caught by codemods.

### Masthead — ⚠️ SIGNIFICANT CHANGE

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| `MastheadBrand` | Direct child of Masthead | **Renamed to `MastheadLogo`**, must be wrapped by new `MastheadBrand` | **Yes** |
| Structure | `MastheadToggle` and `MastheadBrand` as direct children | Must now be wrapped in `MastheadMain` | **Yes** |
| `backgroundColor` | Prop on Masthead | Removed — use theming | **Yes** |

### Text → Content — RENAMED

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Components | `Text`, `TextContent`, `TextList`, `TextListItem` | All replaced by single `Content` component | **Yes** |
| Usage | `<TextContent><Text component="h1">...</Text></TextContent>` | `<Content component="h1">...</Content>` | **Yes** (adds `component` prop where needed) |

### Modal — Promoted from Next

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Import | `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core'` | Old Modal → deprecated path; use new Modal (was ModalNext) | **Yes** |
| ModalNext | `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core/next'` | `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core'` | **Yes** |

### DualListSelector — Promoted from Next

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Import | Old DualListSelector → deprecated path | **Yes** |
| DualListSelectorNext | Promoted to main import path | **Yes** |

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem — Structure Changed

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| API | Many individual props | Everything passed as `children` directly | **Yes** |

### Button — Icon Handling Changed

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Icons | Passed as children (especially for `variant="plain"`) | Must pass to `icon` prop | **Yes** (only for `variant="plain"`) |
| Text wrapping | No wrapper | Button text now wrapped in `<span>` (affects `byText` queries) | **No** — manual test fix |

### AccordionItem — Markup Changed

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Wrapper | No wrapper element | Now renders `div` wrapper | **No** — awareness only |
| `isExpanded` | On AccordionToggle | Moved to AccordionItem | **Yes** |

### PageBreadcrumb / PageSection — Wrapper Logic Changed

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Codemod |
|--------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| `isWidthLimited` | Controlled whether children wrapped in PageBody | No longer controls wrapping | **Yes** |
| New prop | N/A | `hasBodyWrapper` (default: true) | **Yes** (applied with same value as old `isWidthLimited`) |

