## 4. CSS / Token / Variable Changes

### ⚠️ MAJOR: Design Token System Overhaul

PatternFly 6 introduces a completely new **design token system**. This is the single largest migration effort.

#### Token Naming Convention Change

| Aspect | Old (PF5) | New (PF6) |
|--------|-----------|-----------|
| CSS Variable prefix | `--pf-v5-global--*` | `--pf-t--global--*` |
| CSS Variable prefix | `--pf-v5-c-*` (component) | `--pf-v6-c-*` (component) |
| React token prefix | `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| React token import | `@patternfly/react-tokens` | `@patternfly/react-tokens` (same package, new token names) |
| Class prefix | `pf-v5-c-*`, `pf-v5-l-*`, `pf-v5-u-*` | `pf-v6-c-*`, `pf-v6-l-*`, `pf-v6-u-*` |

#### Codemods for Token Updates

| Codemod | What It Does | File Types | Auto-Fix |
|---------|-------------|------------|----------|
| **`class-name-updater --v6`** | Replaces `pf-v5` → `pf-v6` in class names | All | **Yes** |
| **`tokens-update`** | Updates global CSS vars in JS/TSX; marks color tokens with hot pink placeholder | `.js`, `.tsx` | **Partial** — colors need manual replacement |
| **`css-vars-updater`** | Updates CSS vars in non-React files | `.css`, `.scss`, `.md`, etc. | **Partial** |
| **`tokens-prefix-with-t`** | Adds `t_` prefix to React tokens whose value is a `--pf-t` variable | `.js`, `.tsx` | **Yes** |

#### Token Replacement Details

| Category | Behavior | Manual Work? |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| **Global non-color tokens** (spacers, font-size, box-shadow) | Auto-fixed to closest match | Usually no |
| **Global color tokens** | Replaced with `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) / `t_temp_dev_tbd` | **YES — must manually find replacement** |
| **Component tokens** (`--pf-v5-c-*`) | No auto-fix | **YES — manual** |
| **Chart tokens** | No auto-fix | **YES — manual** |

#### Example Token Migrations

| Old (PF5) | New (PF6) | Auto? |
|-----------|-----------|-------|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` | Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--md` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--md` | Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--link--Color--hover` | Must find manually (e.g., context-dependent) | **No** |
| `global_FontSize_lg` (React) | `t_global_font_size_lg` | Yes |
| `global_link_Color_hover` (React) | Must find manually | **No** |

#### CSS Class Name Changes

All PatternFly CSS classes changed prefix:
- Components: `pf-v5-c-*` → `pf-v6-c-*`
- Layouts: `pf-v5-l-*` → `pf-v6-l-*`
- Utilities: `pf-v5-u-*` → `pf-v6-u-*`
- Modifiers: remain `pf-m-*` (unchanged)

#### Logical Direction CSS Changes

| Component | Old CSS Variable | New CSS Variable |
|-----------|-----------------|------------------|
| **SliderStep** | `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` | `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart` |
| **Th/Td sticky** | `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Left` | `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineStart` |
| **Th/Td sticky** | `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Right` | `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineEnd` |

#### Breakpoints Changed to REM

| Breakpoint | Design Token | Old (px) | New (rem) |
|------------|-------------|----------|-----------|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

**Manual work:** Any JavaScript logic using pixel values for breakpoints must be updated.

#### Removed / Added Variable Lists
- [Removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)

