## 9. New Required Patterns

### Theming Changes
- **No more React-side theming props**: `backgroundColor`, `theme`, `variant` (for theming) removed from Masthead, Nav, PageSidebar, etc.
- **Use CSS-based light/dark mode theming** instead

### Button Icon Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<Button variant="plain"><TimesIcon /></Button>

// NEW (PF6)
<Button variant="plain" icon={<TimesIcon />} />
```

### EmptyState Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader
    titleText="Title"
    headingLevel="h2"
    icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />}
  />
  <EmptyStateBody>Body text</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>

// NEW (PF6)
<EmptyState headingText="Title" headingLevel="h2" icon={CubesIcon}>
  <EmptyStateBody>Body text</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

### Masthead Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<Masthead>
  <MastheadToggle><PageToggleButton>...</PageToggleButton></MastheadToggle>
  <MastheadBrand><Brand src="..." alt="Logo" /></MastheadBrand>
  <MastheadContent>...</MastheadContent>
</Masthead>

// NEW (PF6)
<Masthead>
  <MastheadMain>
    <MastheadToggle><PageToggleButton>...</PageToggleButton></MastheadToggle>
    <MastheadBrand>
      <MastheadLogo><Brand src="..." alt="Logo" /></MastheadLogo>
    </MastheadBrand>
  </MastheadMain>
  <MastheadContent>...</MastheadContent>
</Masthead>
```

### Text → Content Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<TextContent>
  <Text component="h1">Title</Text>
  <Text component="p">Paragraph</Text>
  <TextList>
    <TextListItem>Item</TextListItem>
  </TextList>
</TextContent>

// NEW (PF6)
<Content>
  <Content component="h1">Title</Content>
  <Content component="p">Paragraph</Content>
  <Content component="ul">
    <Content component="li">Item</Content>
  </Content>
</Content>
```

### Page masthead Prop
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<Page header={<Masthead>...</Masthead>}>

// NEW (PF6)
<Page masthead={<Masthead>...</Masthead>}>
```

### FormGroup labelHelp Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<FormGroup labelIcon={<Popover>...</Popover>}>

// NEW (PF6)
<FormGroup labelHelp={<FormGroupLabelHelp>...</FormGroupLabelHelp>}>
```

### Popper/Select/Dropdown appendTo Default
The default value of `appendTo` on Dropdown, Select, and Popper has changed to `document.body`.

---

## 10. Test Impact & Breakages

### Button Tests
| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| `aria-disabled` not found | `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attr, not `aria-disabled` (for `component="button"`) | Remove tests expecting `aria-disabled` on standard buttons |
| `byText` query returns wrapper, not button | Button text now wrapped in `<span>` | Use `byRole('button', { name: '...' })` instead of `byText` |

### Select Tests
| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| `byRole` can't find menu options | Popper menu `aria-disabled` after selection (test-only) | Pass `{ hidden: true }` option or set `appendTo="inline"` |

### Markup Changes (Snapshot Updates Required)
These components have changed their internal markup (no API change, but snapshots will break):
- AccordionItem (new `div` wrapper)
- Button (text wrapper `<span>`)
- LoginMainHeader (`div` instead of `header`)
- MenuItemAction (uses Button internally)
- NotificationBadge (stateful button internally)
- NotificationDrawerHeader (`h1` instead of Text)
- Pagination (wrapper around toggle)
- Page (PageBody always wraps when breadcrumb/horizontalSubnav present)
- Tabs scroll buttons
- Toolbar (ToolbarLabelGroupContent markup)
- TreeView (removed `pf-m-selectable` class)
- WizardFooter (ActionList wrapper)
- WizardNavItem (new wrapper element)

