## 11. Codemod Summary

### Running Order
1. **Update package.json** — manual, PF5 → PF6 dependencies
2. **`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6`** — dry run to see issues
3. **`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix`** — auto-fix
4. **`class-name-updater --v6 --fix`** — CSS class prefix updates
5. **`tokens-update`** — React token and CSS variable updates in JS/TSX
6. **`css-vars-updater`** — CSS variable updates in .css/.scss/.md files
7. **Manual cleanup** — hot pink placeholders, component tokens, chart tokens
8. **Repeat steps 2-7** until clean

