## Quick Reference: What Requires MANUAL Work

| Area | Why Manual? |
|------|------------|
| **Color token replacement** | Codemods insert hot pink placeholder (`t_temp_dev_tbd`) — you must choose correct token |
| **Component-level CSS tokens** | No 1:1 mapping; must find equivalent in [PF6 token docs](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens) |
| **Chart CSS tokens** | No auto-fix available |
| **EmptyState complex customizations** | Codemod handles basic cases; complex nesting needs review |
| **Pixel-based breakpoint logic** | Must convert px → rem in JavaScript |
| **CSS overrides using old variables** | Remove or update to new token system |
| **Snapshot tests** | Many markup changes require snapshot regeneration |
| **Button `byText` test queries** | Must switch to `byRole` |
| **Deprecated component replacements** | Codemods move to `/deprecated` but actual replacement (e.g., Chip→Label) may need design review |
| **Custom PatternFly-mimicking CSS** | Must be completely re-skinned |
| **Old Modal/DualListSelector usage** | Moved to deprecated path; recommend migrating to new (promoted) API |
| **DrawerHead + DrawerPanelBody** | No longer composed internally; use independently |
| **Victory chart installation** | Must explicitly install victory peer dependency |

