    content: PatternFly 5→6 Migration Branch Comparison Report
==================================================
Base branch: main
Migration branches: pf-codemods-053126-0120, semver/goose/053026-2257

## Phase 1: Research ✅
- [x] Research PF6 migration guide and breaking changes
- [x] Build migration checklist from official docs

## Phase 2: Establish Baseline ✅
- [x] Get diff stats for each migration branch vs main
- [x] Identify PF-related vs unrelated changes per branch
- [x] Attempt build on each branch

## Phase 3: Branch Analysis ✅
- [x] Migration completeness per branch
- [x] Functional preservation per branch
- [x] Scope discipline per branch
- [x] PF-specific correctness per branch
- [x] Build/compile results per branch
- [x] Risk/maintainability per branch

## Phase 4: Report
- [ ] Score all branches and generate HTML report
- [ ] Save as pf-migration-comparison-report.html

KEY FINDINGS:
- main already has PF6 packages + many PF6 patterns (Content, charts/victory, EmptyState, no pf-v5)
- pf-codemods: 97 files, focused codemod output (Modal→deprecated, hasBodyWrapper, Button icon), BUILDS CLEAN
- semver/goose: 288 files, extensive changes BUT 85 StackItem/SplitItem component= CRASH BUGS, package downgrades, npm install broken
- WINNER: pf-codemods-053126-0120


